    "data": [
        {
            "title": "香港國際七人欖球賽│關天幕下比賽 斐濟男、女子隊旗開得勝",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"香港七欖關天幕下比賽，斐濟男、女子隊旗開得勝。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/59d5e537232c031a73deeeb060ac577f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032815060163436.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">香港七欖關天幕下比賽，斐濟男、女子隊旗開得勝。徐嘉華攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一連3日的香港國際七人欖球賽，今日在啟德主場館展開首天比賽。由於晚上的開幕禮將有激光投影表演，大會一早將天幕關上，擂台躉之一的斐濟沒有此影響。該國男、女隊在隨隊的斐濟球迷熱情帶氣下，都在小組賽旗開得勝。而為斐濟男子隊率先達陣的修度拉加(Filipe Sauturaga)以「完美」來形容首辦香港七欖賽的啟德主場館。\n\n</p><h2>斐濟男子隊首戰贏美國</h2>\n<p>在香港站已取得19冠，同時是巴黎奧運男子七欖銀牌得主的斐濟男子隊，中午出戰A組首場比賽對美國，憑著7號仔修度拉加率先達陣下，以26:17勝美國，下午會再次出場鬥愛爾蘭。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"斐濟女子隊（黑衫）26:17勝愛爾蘭隊。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/279849c6e1e96d69e225771566989715/2025-03/1_21.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        斐濟女子隊（黑衫）26:17勝愛爾蘭隊。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"男子斐濟隊以26:17擊敗美國。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1b90ba1f1a51746bdc68291288f39191/2025-03/2_37.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子斐濟隊以26:17擊敗美國。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"男子斐濟隊以26:17擊敗美國。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aed7b677b6d1b6c874c21278decbd272/2025-03/3_36.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子斐濟隊以26:17擊敗美國。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"男子斐濟隊以26:17擊敗美國。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a63753ecf83a55ed24f7d3c640c12281/2025-03/4_19.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子斐濟隊以26:17擊敗美國。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"斐濟7號仔修度拉加大讚啟德場。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0fc0e90f62c4356213e7668ca649d4c3/2025-03/5_19.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        斐濟7號仔修度拉加大讚啟德場。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>斐濟7號仔大讚啟德場</h2>\n<p>對於球隊的表現，修度拉加信心十足道：「我們今次來就是要拿第20冠，希望在新場可以延續我們斐濟前輩們在香港所做的成績，我們會努力去達成這目標。」同時他亦大讚啟德場：「這裡每一處的設備都很好，球場上蓋關了，打起波來感覺都不錯，我喜歡這裡多於舊場（指香港大球場），這裡甚麼都很新，我都很喜歡，可以說是完美。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"因為晚上的開幕禮將有激光投影表演，關上天幕比賽。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9fe1acf256d3d801ffe468f654567620/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_13_36_49.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        因為晚上的開幕禮將有激光投影表演，關上天幕比賽。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"因為晚上的開幕禮將有激光投影表演，關上天幕比賽。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/52d1466fe7bdc768f8ef04e8b6c1a07e/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_13_44_07.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        因為晚上的開幕禮將有激光投影表演，關上天幕比賽。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>斐濟球迷進駐「北看台」</h2>\n<p>在男子隊出場之前，斐濟女子隊已順利取得分組首勝，她們在B組面對愛爾蘭，輕鬆贏26:17，沒有令在場眾多斐濟球迷失望。首日比賽的早上，入場觀眾未算太多，著名「玩得顛」的「南看台」仍有很多空位，現場最曯目是一班穿起藍衫帶著藍旗的斐濟球迷，他們一如以往進駐「北看台」頭幾排，在比賽時不停為球隊打氣。修度拉加感謝他們道：「粉絲為我們遠道而來香港，好多謝他們。」記者/攝影：徐嘉華\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"斐濟球迷一早進駐北看台。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ee761d42fceab6e0112b3433cb981929/2025-03/6_20.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        斐濟球迷一早進駐北看台。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"斐濟球迷一早進駐北看台。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e389fcfea1ac69ddcb45fc611a1835bd/2025-03/7_16.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        斐濟球迷一早進駐北看台。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"南看台上球迷數目不多。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/11196b1ee4c5a5ffa7b7ba8c7b865d06/2025-03/8_8.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        南看台上球迷數目不多。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"南看台上球迷數目不多。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1aac6552dcc3bb376d717fed9b11b542/2025-03/9_11.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        南看台上球迷數目不多。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"周五早上，入場球迷不算太多。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ad1dfd9307f335518af1676909ffd21e/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_13_49_12.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        周五早上，入場球迷不算太多。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"周五早上，入場球迷不算太多。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c43f3391d410c729f4cab1144f3fdf5/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_14_24_30.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        周五早上，入場球迷不算太多。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060767/即時-體育-香港國際七人欖球賽│關天幕下比賽-斐濟男-女子隊旗開得勝",
